DESCRIPTION:The evil Empire has fallen\, and Imperial warlords remain scat
 tered throughout the galaxy. As the fledgling New Republic works to protec
 t everything the Rebellion fought for\, they have enlisted the help of leg
 endary Mandalorian bounty hunter Din Djarin (Pedro Pascal) and his young a
 pprentice Grogu. Directed by Jon Favreau\, “The Mandalorian and Grogu”
  also stars Sigourney Weaver and is produced by Jon Favreau\, Kathleen Ken
 nedy\, Dave Filoni\, and Ian Bryce\, with music composed by Ludwig Görans
 son.
